    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245080/extras/67f799847c13a2e00a307d7a8db004ef.poster.avif?t=1761070135\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245080/extras/67f799847c13a2e00a307d7a8db004ef.webm?t=1761070135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245080/extras/67f799847c13a2e00a307d7a8db004ef.mp4?t=1761070135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5th Catacylsm is a JRPG-style Deckbuilder hybrid featuring randomly generated loot, enemies, and a dungeon to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245080/extras/860451bc1085f4dfa4878cc99e054f87.poster.avif?t=1761070135\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245080/extras/860451bc1085f4dfa4878cc99e054f87.webm?t=1761070135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245080/extras/860451bc1085f4dfa4878cc99e054f87.mp4?t=1761070135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The city of New Babel lies on a cursed mountain, which swallows the cities built atop it and grows ever taller. The residual magic of the curse imbues objects with ever greater magical power the longer they are exposed to it, and give greater power the closer to the source those objects reside. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve into the entombed ruins of the old cities, battle creatures of the deep, and find treasures beyond your wildest dreams. Return to the surface to sell off expensive trinkets and fund an even further expedition!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245080/extras/7e36633dc8a2acac6f259941964d911d.poster.avif?t=1761070135\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245080/extras/7e36633dc8a2acac6f259941964d911d.webm?t=1761070135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245080/extras/7e36633dc8a2acac6f259941964d911d.mp4?t=1761070135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomly generated cards to find and strategize with.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many enemies to fight with randomly generated attributes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A multi-tiered, intricate dungeon to explore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shopping!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dungeon crawling twist on the traditional Deckbuilder formula.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245080/extras/18d8d54242d684a2a2295e01ad9308e4.poster.avif?t=1761070135\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245080/extras/18d8d54242d684a2a2295e01ad9308e4.webm?t=1761070135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245080/extras/18d8d54242d684a2a2295e01ad9308e4.mp4?t=1761070135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
